author: abcoathup
content: There is an EIP Editing office hours https://github.com/ethereum-cat-herders/EIPIP/issues/234

author: anndressa_cabral
content: Yes, for EIP 18 #234 editing file. This proposal has already been accepted and now they are discussing improvements, is that it? Because I haven't sent my proposal yet, but I would like to participate in the call, is that possible?

author: samwilsn
content:
The issue linked there isn't an EIP itself, but an agenda for our biweekly call for authors to connect with editors and ask questions.

We'd love it if you came out on <t:1685458800:f> if you have any questions about the process!
